<html>
<head>
<title>Bulletins on Town Hall</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<center>
<h2>Listservs on Town Hall</h2>
</center>

<form action="/townhall/scripts/all-list-handler.cgi" method="post">

Select the lists you'd like to join by clicking in the appropriate box, fill in the information below, and click the "Sign me up!" button below.  That's all there is to it!
<p>
<form action="/townhall/scripts/th-list-handler.cgi" method="post"> 
<input type="checkbox" name="i-th-quote" checked><b>Conservative Quote of the Day</b><br>
Start your morning off right with wisdom from historical and contemporary conservatives. This daily e-mail will be kept short, and may include a small programming note.  -- <a href="/townhall/listserv/townhall/unsubscribe.html">Unsubscribe</a>
<p>
<input type="checkbox" name="i-th-pamph" checked><b>Town Hall Pamphlet</b><br>
This list will alert you to new developments at Town Hall.  These will include the addition of new Citizen Organizations, major milestones, new and improved features, and more.  -- <a href="/townhall/listserv/townhall/unsubscribe.html">Unsubscribe</a><p>

<input type="checkbox" name="i-frc-wwatch" checked><b>FRC Washington Watch Notification</b><br>
This list will keep you abrest of new issues of FRC's <i>Washington Watch</i>. It covers developments in Washington that affect families' daily lives.<p>

<input type="checkbox" name="i-frc-bauer" checked><b>FRC Gary Bauer Monthly Newsletter</b><br>
Now you can receive a monthly newsletter from FRC's president, Gary Bauer.<p>

<input type="checkbox" name="i-frc-ed" checked><b>FRC Ed Facts</b>
Here you will learn about breaking developments in education in Washington and around the nation in a weekly update.<p>

<input type="checkbox" name="i-frc-press" checked><b>FRC Press Releases</b><br>
Receive FRC Press Releases, covering all of FRC attempts to defend the traditional family system.<p>

<input type="checkbox" name="i-frc-family" checked><b>FRC Family Policy Notification</b><br>
Receive notice when a new issue of the bimonthly FRC <i>Family Policy</i> is avaliable. It offers policy advice about some of our nations most serious social problems.<p> 

<input type="checkbox" name="i-savers-update" checked><b>Savers and Investers League Update</b><br>
Keep up to date on the impact of taxes on private investment.<p>

<input type="checkbox" name="i-heritage-update" checked><b>Heritage Foundation Update</b><br>
Stay abrest of what's new at Heritage with this weekly letter. You'll find out about new policy papers, pannel discussions, and Top 10 Facts of the week.<p>

<P>
<INPUT TYPE = "TEXT" NAME="a-first">  First Name<BR> 
