<DOCHDR>
http://www.empower.org:80/abic/letters/letter-3.html.cgi 204.71.237.79 19970210052009 text/html 7318
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 05:20:54 GMT
